high_descs: Turn right and go to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, take out the empty bowl, and close the refrigerator door.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Place the bowl into the right side of the sink, turn the water on, fill the bowl with water, turn the water off, and pick up the bowl of water.
Turn to your left and go to the lower cabinet that is under the toaster. Open the cabinet door.
Place the bowl of water in the cabinet, on the right area of the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl full of water into the cabinet under the toaster.

high_descs: Open refrigerator, pick up bowl to the right of the potato.  Close refrigerator.
Place bowl in sink, fill bowl with water.
Turn left, proceed to cabinet under counter.
Open left cabinet, put bowl of water in cabinet, close door.
anns.task_desc: Move bowl from refrigerator to sink, fill with water then place in cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward to the fridge
Open the fridge and pick up the bowl from the shelf inside
Turn around and walk forward to the sink
Wash the bowl under water in sink and remove it
Turn left and walk up to the cabinet just right of the stove
Open the bottom cabinet nearest the stove and put the bowl in it
anns.task_desc: Put the washed bowl in the kitchen cabinet
